card.text:
Choose one —
• Destroy target land.
• Add {R}{R}{R}{R}{R}

Whenever you choose one or more modes, put that many charge counters on this Equipment.
Equipped creature gets +X/+X and has vigilance, where X is the number of charge counters on this Equipment.
Equip {3}

When Creativity enters, look at the top seven cards of your library. Put one of them into your graveyard, one of them into your hand, and the rest on the bottom of your library in a random order.
At the beginning of your end step, create a 1/1 Incarnation creature token named Soul that is all colors for each Incarnation in your graveyard.
Evoke {5}
